title: I’m Not a Regressor
description: I’m Not a Regressor Manhwa 나는 회귀자가 아닙니다 One day, a silver-haired goddess appeared before me. [The star of the heaven rebellion. The one who goes against fate. The only savior of a world that is fated to end.] Woman, what are you even talking about? [You are the regressor, huh?] What? I’m not one, though…
